Tags in Ansible
---------------

- include: webserver.yml
  tags: web
- include: dbserver.yml
  tags: db
  
Then run the following command to only run the respective tagged playbooks
anisble-playbook web --tags web site.yml   # This will only run the tasks with the respective web tags added to it
  
Ansible Galaxy
--------------
Download
Share
Review

Installing Galaxy roles
---------
ansible-galaxy install username.role
Downloading a role from the ansible galaxy 
ansible-galaxy install username.docker  # These commands are available on the ansible galaxy itself
